General.Name: Crown Energy AB (publ)
General.Description: Crown Energy AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, operates in the oil, gas, and real estate industries with operations focused on underexplored areas in Africa and the Middle East. The company operates through two segments, Asset Development and Management, and Energy. The Asset Development and Management segment provides customized residential and office lease solutions, and associated services to the energy industry. Its services include design and construction, leasing, and property management, as well as other value-added services, such as security, transport, and telecommunications. The Energy segment develops and explores oil assets in early stages for recoverable reserves in South Africa, Madagascar, and Iraq. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Crown Energy AB (publ) is a subsidiary of YBE Ventures Ltd.
